🤖 Sumo Robot Project - 3kg Category
This repository documents the development, logic, and hardware design of our 3kg Mega Sumo Robot, developed as part of our robotics engineering projects.

🏆 Project Achievements
Our team successfully secured 9th place in the MRC Magnetic Mega Sumo 3kg competition, which qualified us for the Global Finals in Greece.

📂 Repository Structure
/body: Contains the hardware design and chassis construction details.

/final_sumo_logic: Contains the core programming and logic for the robot's autonomous behavior.

FINAL_Waslleh_Sumo_3kg_List: Procurement and parts list for the robot.

Schedule: Project timeline and competition preparation phases.

التأهل لليونان: Official qualification documentation.

🛠 Tech Stack
Hardware: Arduino/Microcontrollers, Infrared Sensor Arrays (QTR-8A), Mechanical Switches.

Design & Fabrication: Advanced hardware design, 3D printing (Bambu Studio).

Programming: C++/Arduino Logic.

👥 The Team
This project is a collaborative effort by our robotics team: Raghad Alshrawneh, Renad, Shaza.
